    • Field Detail

      • SCHEMA_VERSION

        @NonNull
public static final java.lang.String SCHEMA_VERSION
        If the DB schema changes, and this can lead to breaking compatibility with older DB versions, this schema version should be updated, and a schema migration should be devised in order to do not break backup restore functionality. In order to be properly uploaded to the backend, the version must follow this pattern ^[0-9]+.[0-9]+.[0-9]+$
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
